headlines.description: Jos Mara Gimnez scored a header deep into stoppage time as Atltico Madrid snatched a 2-1 home victory over Inter Milan in the Champions League.
headlines.shortLinkText: Gimnez heads Atleti to late win over Inter Milan

headlines.description: The crisis affecting Liverpool deepened with a calamitous 4-1 Champions League home defeat to PSV Eindhoven.
headlines.shortLinkText: Liverpool slump deepens with home rout by PSV

headlines.description: Kylian Mbapp helped himself to the second fastest hat-trick in Champions League history and four goals in total as Real Madrid came from behind to beat Olympiacos 4-3 in Piraeus.
headlines.shortLinkText: Madrid hold off Olympiacos with Mbapp's 4 goals

headlines.description: A hat trick by Paris Saint-Germain midfielder Vitinha consigned Tottenham Hotspur to another defeat on Wednesday.
headlines.shortLinkText: Vitinha hat trick helps PSG overpower Spurs
